FEMUR

femur is the longest bone in fadriel's body, running from hip to knee in each leg
it is the primary lever arm of locomotion: every step, every jump, every running stride pivots through the femur
femur is also a major marrow vault, producing red blood cells throughout fadriel's life
it is built to bear extraordinary load without breaking, which is why its shaft is dense and tubular

